<para><emphasis role="bold">poly-L-lysine coated slides</emphasis></para>
<orderedlist numeration="arabic">
<listitem><para>Immerse glass slides in solution of kitchen detergent for 20 min</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Wash in tap water for 1 hr</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Wash in ion-exchanged water</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Autoclave and dry at 80 &deg;C</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Drop poly-L-lysine solution (SIGMA P-8920) onto individual wells of the slides</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Leave for 25 min</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Aspirate off the excess solution (only when 3-well slides are used)</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>Dry at 65 &deg;C for 1 hr</para></listitem></orderedlist>
